{"name":"Recorder’s Sentencing","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You put your deity’s varied sentencings on display.</p>\n<p>Choose two sentence cantrips from other inquisitions. <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">You gain these sentence cantrips. Additionally, once per day, you can amp a sentence cantrip without spending a Focus Point.</span></p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"recorders-sentencing","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Recorder Dedication"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686605783672,"modifiedTime":1686623844673,"lastModifiedBy":"5wWA7yb814llroUu"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"3RrykrCbM2xLCShv"}
{"name":"Recorder Dedication","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>Your deity expands your ability to dispense their judgments. You gain the @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.spells.tRdzRXd0Ff56FNwR]{Ongoing Judgment} focus spell and increase your focus pool by 1 Focus Point.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Special </strong>You cannot select another dedication feat until you have gained two other feats from the @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.journals.BEh05svyLH0iRXfU.JournalEntryPage.vWyCFmVNSHetPMKB]{Recorder} archetype.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[{"key":"ActiveEffectLike","mode":"add","path":"system.resources.focus.max","value":1}],"slug":"recorder-dedication","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":2},"traits":{"value":["archetype","class","dedication"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"recorder’s judgments"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.CkC1OiKinRKYIsv3"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686605783672,"modifiedTime":1686623720112,"lastModifiedBy":"5wWA7yb814llroUu"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"64rFVTlK6vMoXSoW"}
{"name":"Piercing Condemnation","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You hone your strikes against the foes of your faith.</p>\n<p>When you deal additional damage against a @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.effects.xg3c12QeyDmDQHG9]{Claimant} as described in @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.actions.q4HzZswft1Hu11sC]{Judge}, you also deal 1d4 precision damage , increasing to 1d6 at 6th level.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[{"category":"precision","diceNumber":1,"value":{"brackets":[{"end":5,"value":{"dieSize":"d4"}},{"start":6,"value":{"dieSize":"d6"}}]},"key":"DamageDice","predicate":["target:effect:claimant","self:effect:condemnation"],"selector":"strike-damage"}],"slug":"piercing-condemnation","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Recorder Dedication"},{"value":"a condemnation judgment"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5FI9cOSI7p1WruuI"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686605783672,"modifiedTime":1686623827571,"lastModifiedBy":"5wWA7yb814llroUu"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"CEb7YJ2n0NMEZrd3"}
{"name":"Recorder’s Judgments","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>If you take this class feature, you must take @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.recorder-class-archetype.64rFVTlK6vMoXSoW]{Recorder Dedication} as your 2nd-level class feat.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> inquisitor class</p>\n<p><strong>Recorder Adjustments:</strong> You don’t gain spell slots or add spells to your spell repertoire except cantrips. You still gain inquisition spells slots and add the listed spells to your spell repertoire.</p>\n<p>You gain an additional 1st-level judgment feat of your choice. At every odd level, you gain your choice of a judgment feat or a skill feat whose prerequisites you meet.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"recorders-judgments","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"inquisitor class"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686605783672,"modifiedTime":1686607311298,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"IoOAkNNQfjrPj5EN"}
{"name":"Recorder’s Senses","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You take careful record of all around you. Increase your proficiency rank for Perception to master. At 12th level, when you roll a success on a Perception check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.BlAOM2X92SI6HMtJ]{Seek} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.1xRFPTFtWtGJ9ELw]{Sense Motive}, you get a critical success instead, and when creatures fail at @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.ewwCglB7XOPLUz72]{Lying} to you or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VMozDqMMuK5kpoX4]{Sneaking} against you, they critically fail, instead. At 16th level, increase your proficiency with Perception to legendary.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[{"key":"ActiveEffectLike","mode":"upgrade","path":"system.attributes.perception.rank","value":{"brackets":[{"end":15,"value":3},{"start":16,"value":4}],"field":"actor|system.details.level.value"}},{"key":"Note","outcome":["success"],"selector":"perception","text":"When you roll a success on a Perception check to Seek or Sense Motive, you get a critical success instead.","title":"{item|name}","predicate":[{"or":["action:seek","action:sense-motive"]}]},{"adjustment":{"success":"one-degree-better"},"predicate":[{"or":["action:seek","action:sense-motive"]}],"key":"AdjustDegreeOfSuccess","selector":"perception","type":"attribute"}],"slug":"recorders-senses","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":8},"traits":{"value":["archetype"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"class","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Recorder Dedication"},{"value":"expert in Perception"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.zXPlfEiMyY7ntIDO"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686605783672,"modifiedTime":1686623885007,"lastModifiedBy":"5wWA7yb